               <msContents>
                  <summary>This is a versified work in 220 couplets on definitions of Arabic words into Persian, corresponding couplets to Persian poetical and metrical measures. The number of couplets is recorded differently in the references. This work has been used to teach Arabic in Iran, India and Turkey as lately as the recent centuries. It has been printed several times in Iran.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="WadhMinasian_713-item1">
                     <textLang mainLang="fa">Persian</textLang>
                     <note type="content-genre">Dictionary</note>
                     <title xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc">Niṣāb al-Ṣibyān</title>
                     <title xml:lang="fa">نصاب الصبیان</title>
                     
                     
                     <author key="no2006071896‏" ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/56368539">‎Farāhī, Abū Naṣr Muḥammad Badr al-Dīn‏‏فراهی، ابونصر محمد بدرالدینAbū Naṣr Farāhī, Masʿūd bin Abī Bakr (640 Qamarī/1242)ابونصر فراهی، مسعود بن ابی بکر (۶۴۰ ق/۱۲۴۲م)<addName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" type="laqab"/>
                        
                        <addName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" type="kunyah"/>
                        
                        
                        
                     </author>
                     <incipit xml:lang="fa" defective="true">… ما حرکت الشمال النخل الدقیق و تحرکت الشمال لنخل الدقیق که چون صبیان را…</incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="fa">… باد اندر جوار رحمت حق/پدر و مادر و معلم ما.</explicit>
                     <colophon xml:lang="fa">تمت النصاب بعون الملک الوهاب.</colophon>
